# {{.Name}}

A Unity game powered by Mizu backend.

## Requirements

- Unity 2022.3 LTS or later
- .NET Framework 4.7.1 or later
- Mizu backend server

## Getting Started

1. Open the project in Unity Hub
2. Open the `Bootstrap` scene from `Assets/_Project/Scenes/`
3. Configure your Mizu backend URL in the GameManager
4. Press Play to run the game

