- Build > Build Android
- Build > Build iOS
- Build > Build WebGL
- Build > Build Windows
- Build > Build macOS

## API Reference

### GameManager

```csharp
// Start the game
await GameManager.Instance.StartGameAsync();

// Pause/Resume
GameManager.Instance.PauseGame();
GameManager.Instance.ResumeGame();

// End game with score
await GameManager.Instance.EndGameAsync(1000);
```

### Leaderboards

```csharp
// Submit score
await GameManager.Instance.Leaderboards.SubmitScoreAsync("main", 1000);

// Get top scores
var scores = await GameManager.Instance.Leaderboards.GetTopScoresAsync("main", 10);
```

### Achievements

```csharp
// Unlock achievement
await GameManager.Instance.Achievements.UnlockAsync("first_win");

// Update progress
await GameManager.Instance.Achievements.UpdateProgressAsync("play_10_games", 5);
```

### Analytics

```csharp
// Track custom event
GameManager.Instance.Analytics.Track("level_start", new Dictionary<string, object>
{
    ["level_id"] = "level_1"
});
```

